{"tid":1460970,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"將你嘅不滿化佢文字 施政報告2019","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:50:05.000Z","uid":142252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3eb1469083d995ffb77d34c263fd4aeb40a4696","tid":1460970,"uid":142252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.policyaddress.gov.hk/consultation19/chi/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.policyaddress.gov.hk%2Fconsultation19%2Fchi%2Findex.html&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y94oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=de9d14d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.policyaddress.gov.hk/consultation19/chi/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2019施政報告接受大家意見<br />\n點解冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是時候 將你嘅不滿及你嘅期望寫比條7婆<br />\n<br />\n為咗顯示大家質素，唔該大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好寫粗口、唔好人身攻擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為大家都send template只會比人Ignore,<br />\n麻煩大家食完飯或番到屋企，用少少時間表達意見！<br />\n唔單止反送中，重有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每日150隻蝗</span></span></strong>呢？重有所謂嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與年輕人connect</span></strong>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>房屋政策</strong></span>等都可以講。<br />\n<br />\n自己係呢方面唔太擅長，有巴絲有更好建議或內容 請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e506d470ba95642652957fd12f332d36615a07a","tid":1460970,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7e4423fde657f2f3934d08f7d35d6c7b244b22","tid":1460970,"uid":220673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"f3b34539c003434f19368161cdebfd92968bda1f","tid":1460970,"uid":61840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0